  "headline": "Public Health Basics",
  "description": "Public health focuses on preventing disease and promoting health at population level — in contrast to clinical medicine's individual focus. Core functions: assessment (monitor health), policy development, assurance (ensure access). Key achievements: vaccination, sanitation, tobacco control, motor vehicle safety, infectious disease control.",
